# Python

This repository uses `uv` for dependency management, so Python code should always be run with `uv run` (e.g., `uv run some_script.py`).

Dependencies can be added like `uv add dependency_name`, or all dependencies listed in `pyproject.toml` can be installed with `uv sync`.